# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules
#
# Intentionally empty. Astro builds in directory format
# (dist/blog/slug/index.html), and Cloudflare Pages serves those with
# trailing slashes as the canonical URL. Any trailing-slash-stripping rule
# here conflicts with CF's built-in directory canonicalisation and creates
# an infinite redirect loop. See decision-log 2026-04-17.
#
# Reference: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
